71: **Decision:** Rename product-facing and internal identity from ClaudeMeter to Pinemeter in M001 where feasible, including code symbols, tests, docs/site, project/target/scheme names, and metadata.
73: **Rationale:** The user wants to take ownership of the codebase, not merely repaint the UI. Leaving internal ClaudeMeter assumptions creates future confusion and makes the repo less presentable.
